title: The Knights "Clocks On Hold" - Converse Rubber Tracks: Track Of The Week
description:
The single "Clocks On Hold" by The Knights is this week's "Track of the Week". Recorded at the Converse Rubber Tracks studio in Hamburg, the four members of the band entered the studio, worked on perfecting their song arrangement, and experimented with different recording techniques.

For more on Converse Rubber Tracks, check out:
www.converse.com/rubbertracks
